abstract: National Association of Realtors notes drop in pending home sales index, indicating that growth in housing market could be slowing.
lead_paragraph: Contracts to buy previously owned homes fell in November for the third time in four months, a signal that growth in the housing market could be cooling.

headline.main: Pending U.S. Home Sales Declined Again in November
